{"descriptions":[{"id":1054,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp\u003eExamples of its use: ཡག་ག, ཡག་ཤོས་, སྙིང་རྗེ་པ་ལ་, ཆེ་དྲགས་, རིང་ལོས་\u003c/p\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":false,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:12:11 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:12:11 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]},{"id":1055,"title":null,"content":"\u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eGenerally speaking, adjectives strongly resemble verbs and may even be \u0026ldquo;conjugated\u0026rdquo; with certain auxiliary verbs. Adjectives usually consist of a radical and a suffix, or else a doubled radical.\u003c/p\u003e \u003cp class=\"Paragraph\"\u003eThere are a number of suffixes that specify the degree of the adjective. These include:\u003c/p\u003e \u003cul\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔོ་\u003c/span\u003e Positive\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔ་\u003c/span\u003e Comparative\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཤོས་\u003c/span\u003e Superlative and intensive\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཔ་ལ་\u003c/span\u003e Admirative\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eདྲགས་\u003c/span\u003e Excessive\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཙམ་\u003c/span\u003e Attenuative\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eཐག་ཆོད་\u003c/span\u003e or \u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eསའི་\u003c/span\u003e Intensives\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003e\u003cspan class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\"\u003eལོས་\u003c/span\u003e Interrogative\u003c/li\u003e \u003cli\u003eExpressive suffixes\u003c/li\u003e \u003c/ul\u003e","source_url":null,"is_primary":true,"created_at":"2013-09-15 04:12:11 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:12:11 UTC","authors":[{"id":"6","fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre"}]}]}